title: Thales Payshield 10K NTP
agents: snmp
catalog: hw/Payshield
license: Proprietary
distribution: Proprietary
description:
 This check monitors the NTP (Network Time Protocol) configuration and status of a Thales Payshield HSM via SNMP. It reports whether NTP is enabled, the list of configured NTP servers, their status, offset, stratum, and other synchronization details.

 The output of the check plugin provides:
 - NTP enabled/disabled status
 - NTP server IP addresses
 - NTP offset (ms)
 - NTP stratum
 - NTP peer status

 Long output of the check plugin provides:
 - NTP synchronization status
 - NTP server details
 - Last update time

inventory:
 This check does not create inventory entries.
